---
const outputs = [
  {
    label: 'ICP profiles',
    description: 'Your best customers, prioritized by product fit'
  },
  {
    label: 'Value moments',
    description: 'The moments that make users stay, tiered by impact'
  },
  {
    label: 'Activation map',
    description: '4-level spectrum with measurable triggers'
  },
  {
    label: 'Measurement specs',
    description: 'Every event, property, and dimension you should track'
  }
];
---

<section class="section-padding">
  <div class="container-content">
    <h2 class="heading-2 text-center mb-6">
      What if the growth model engineered itself?
    </h2>

    <p class="body-text text-center mb-12">
      Basesignal scans your product's public presence — marketing site, pricing page, docs — and generates structured growth intelligence automatically.
    </p>

    <!-- Output Cards -->
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-12">
      {outputs.map((output) => (
        <div class="card">
          <h3 class="text-text-primary font-medium mb-1">{output.label}</h3>
          <p class="text-text-secondary text-sm">{output.description}</p>
        </div>
      ))}
    </div>

    <!-- Conclusion -->
    <p class="body-text text-center max-w-2xl mx-auto">
      From a URL. In 60 seconds. No data required.<br />
      <span class="text-accent font-medium">What took consulting teams two weeks now takes a single command.</span>
    </p>
  </div>
</section>
